LDK Solar Said to Hire Morgan Stanley For Sale of Dollar Bonds

-- B y   K a t r i n a   N i c h o l a s
-- 
2011-04-29T10:01:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-29/china-s-ldk-solar-said-to-hire-morgan-stanley-for-sale-of-dollar-bonds.html
LDK Solar Co., a Chinese maker of
solar energy products, hired Morgan Stanley to help it with a
proposed sale of dollar bonds, according to a person familiar
with the matter.  The Reg S/144A notes may be sold after meetings with credit
investors in the U.S.,  Hong Kong , Singapore and London which
start on May 3, the person said, asking not to be identified as
details are private.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Katrina Nicholas at 
 knicholas2@bloomberg.net  